== Introduction
This guide will help the user of the data historian in understanding the platform,
of its installation, its use. The data historian having been designed with a view to
deployment on a Big Data infrastructure, which is by nature an environment
complex to implement, we will only cover deployments in this guide
on a single machine and gradually.
For a deployment on a multi-server Big Data infrastructure and its security, it will be necessary
refer to other documentation or contact Hurence at contact@hurence.com. Hurence
will typically be able to help you scale your initial single-server infrastructure.
